com.ebay.sdk.call
Class ValidateTestUserRegistrationCall

java.lang.Object
  com.ebay.sdk.ApiCall
      com.ebay.sdk.call.ValidateTestUserRegistrationCall

public class ValidateTestUserRegistrationCall
extends ApiCall

Wrapper class of the ValidateTestUserRegistration call of eBay SOAP API.

Title: SOAP API wrapper library.

Description: Contains wrapper classes for eBay SOAP APIs.

Copyright: Copyright (c) 2009

Company: eBay Inc.


Input property: FeedbackStore - Value for the feedback score of a user. If no value is passed in the request, or if the value is zero, the feedback score is unchanged. This element is not intended for regularly testing feedback because the feedback value can change after the request.
Input property: RegistrationDate - Value for the date and time that a user's registration begins.
Input property: SubscribeSA - Indicates if a user subscribes to Seller's Assistant. You cannot request to subscribe a user to both Seller's Assistant and Seller's Assistant Pro. You cannot request to unsubscribe a user.
Input property: SubscribeSAPro - Indicates if a user subscribes to Seller's Assistant Pro. You cannot request to subscribe a user to both Seller's Assistant and Seller's Assistant Pro. You cannot request to unsubscribe a user.
Input property: SubscribeSM - Indicates if a user subscribes to Selling Manager. You cannot request to subscribe a user to both Selling Manager and Selling Manager Pro. You cannot request to unsubscribe a user.
Input property: SubscribeSMPro - Indicates if a user subscribes to Selling Manager Pro. You cannot request to subscribe a user to both Selling Manager and Selling Manager Pro. You cannot request to unsubscribe a user.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Ron Murphy
